column2: "...Stop. She's coming. Stay alert."
"...so it was you. No wonder I wasn't able to sense my precious children."
"You've taken such sweet care of them... you impudent bastards."
"My friend was right. Pick on her family, and she'll rear her ugly face!"
"...you were looking for me? Little girl, do you even know who I am?"
"Naturally. Dark Falz 【Apprentice】, I presume?。"
"Queen of the insect horde, specializing in Blitzkrieg operations. Did I leave anything out, Mrs. Falz?"
"Fufu...fwaHAHA! Couldn't have said it better myself!"
"But tell me this, child. Do you REALLY know what Dark Falz is?"
"Of course."
"My sworn enemy."
"...Hmph. Not fast enough."
"...My, my. So quick to violence. Do you ARKS attack everyone without warning?"
"What are you complaining about, coward? If you're going to attack us, let's get this over with!"
"...I'll pass, thank you. Child, I'll find you a more appropriate way to die."
"...she's gone. Quite talkative for a Darker, isn't she?"
"1. Are you all right?"
"2. What were you thinking, fighting alone!?"
"What, you're worried about me? Teehee...thank you."
"I'm just fine. You don't need to concern yourself with me."
"I provoked her on purpose. Her attitude showed it worked. She'll be focused only on me."
"B-but wait! Until I defeat her, that means...it will be dangerous for anyone around me."
"I won't be able to enjoy any more conversations! Ugh...I'm so stupid."
"I know! All I have to do is take her down, pronto! Yeah, that's it!"
"The sooner, the better! Gotta run!"
